name: Animals of Low Moral Standing Print by R.S. Posnak
description: Ever notice how we apply human judgements to our animal friends? Are scavengers "bad"? Are cute fluffy herbivores "good"? This poster by R.S. Posnak raises the subject of anthropomorphism in a humorous and aesthetically pleasing way. 12" x 18" Giclee print on high quality archival paper. Check out the print that goes with it: Animals of High Moral Standing. These are shipped in a sturdy tube. For domestic shipping, these are shipped Priority mail. For international, they are shipped First Class international.
